ornelli, who=E2=80=99s
retiring after 38 years of covering the league for CBS and Fox. Cornelli, w=
ho has been on the lead NFL crew dating back to John Madden=E2=80=99s days =
at CBS, is known for running up and down the sidelines with his handheld ca=
mera. Incredibly well-liked by Fox=E2=80=99s production staff, he grew emot=
ional during Thursday=E2=80=99s camera meeting when director Rich Russo hon=
ored him. =E2=80=9CThe greatest handheld camera person in the history of wh=
